1:28:54.285 --> 1:28:55.504
Can you hear me?

1:28:55.678 --> 1:28:56.809
Tommy! Akiko!

1:28:56.983 --> 1:28:58.289
Shit!

1:29:29.581 --> 1:29:30.843
