1:29:31.017 --> 1:29:32.671
Nothing matters
but the safety of the clan.

1:29:32.845 --> 1:29:34.064
You are the clan!

1:29:34.238 --> 1:29:36.153
I am nothing by myself.

1:30:48.181 --> 1:30:49.835
I guess the party started early.

1:31:13.337 --> 1:31:16.166
He needs help.He deserves to die.

1:33:07.886 --> 1:33:10.976
We have to stop Kenta.
He has the Jewel.

1:33:16.416 --> 1:33:18.462
This isn'’t over.

1:33:29.821 --> 1:33:32.607
