1:35:54.879 --> 1:35:55.880
Die.

1:35:58.709 --> 1:36:00.972
We'’re under attack!
It'’s Tommy.

1:36:05.890 --> 1:36:06.891
Snake.

1:36:14.072 --> 1:36:16.683
You'’re in a tight spot, huh?I'’ve been in worse.

1:36:16.858 --> 1:36:19.077
