1:37:02.077 --> 1:37:03.774
Yeah. For them.

1:37:31.628 --> 1:37:33.064
Snake Eyes,

1:37:33.238 --> 1:37:36.502
betray our trust again,
I'’ll kill you myself.

1:37:38.156 --> 1:37:39.592
