in any capacity.

1:47:44.066 --> 1:47:45.328
"Serve"?

1:47:50.420 --> 1:47:51.682
Serve?

1:47:54.729 --> 1:47:59.516
I have given my life
to this clan!

1:47:59.690 --> 1:48:01.953
